{"tid":1927314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳男子商場昏迷無呼吸　護士兼區議員急救﹕遲幾分鐘生存率低","createTime":"2020-03-15T17:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T00:22:30.000Z","uid":81228,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7a3a92b78c7ef715c6ac5fb9eeac45baa86f7a","tid":1927314,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒（俗稱武漢肺炎）疫情持續，近月網上流傳不少街頭有人暈倒吐血、嘔吐的照片，有時未必有人即時救援，而昨日（14日）將軍澳彩明商場亦有人倒地昏迷，眉角流血，更失去呼吸脈搏，不少人圍觀，但無人上前救援。幸註冊護士兼中西區區議員任嘉兒途經上址，為傷者進行心外壓急救，直至救護員到場。<br />\n<br />\n疫情下巿民即使見到有人倒地，但可能因憂心而卻步不敢救人，任嘉兒指留意到國內外，甚至香港有不少暈倒失救情況，但許多患者是中風、心臟病發，「遲幾分鐘，生存機率會降低！」。她指救人是分秒必爭，呼籲港人報讀急救課程，遇緊急情況時方能伸出援手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4159571/org/87260a2135483ac0756eb56c6b34b3da.png/DkxCQ28axwCeZV5-YglCxan-XHxGMVyPOz9JFjs_SRY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4159571%2Forg%2F87260a2135483ac0756eb56c6b34b3da.png%2FDkxCQ28axwCeZV5-YglCxan-XHxGMVyPOz9JFjs_SRY&h=796fd8a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中西區區議員任嘉兒為傷者進行心外壓，當救護員到場時便交由他們接手。（網民Miki Lau上傳）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4159588/org/2a956a9aaf14f4891545fdc437561fb8.jpg/jTqLG-dbDr-kEzrfZHhYzjU7FiO2ACj7YU5fo2FOX6M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4159588%2Forg%2F2a956a9aaf14f4891545fdc437561fb8.jpg%2FjTqLG-dbDr-kEzrfZHhYzjU7FiO2ACj7YU5fo2FOX6M&h=b8ce67dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4159586/org/2020ebe559d25ea1076ca384d1d45e43.jpg/1NmGuRgqcgCErFnFel9dBVjmm-jD_QedqB5e0KgeXtA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4159586%2Forg%2F2020ebe559d25ea1076ca384d1d45e43.jpg%2F1NmGuRgqcgCErFnFel9dBVjmm-jD_QedqB5e0KgeXtA&h=1dd31d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4159590/org/c6dc824f15ba7b5780ba8ac8bf8f5102.jpg/UlgP-yDmcJRWfOUdzdUTDAzKTVRcitTNJ_d3Lg33dy4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4159590%2Forg%2Fc6dc824f15ba7b5780ba8ac8bf8f5102.jpg%2FUlgP-yDmcJRWfOUdzdUTDAzKTVRcitTNJ_d3Lg33dy4&h=fe539deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4159587/org/307a4f76ddfb3f609e7313b2705d2146.jpg/uOMwc5QkL_KZb9sdrBpj9ngN_TCMbk7iqSgWQKkoFkA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4159587%2Forg%2F307a4f76ddfb3f609e7313b2705d2146.jpg%2FuOMwc5QkL_KZb9sdrBpj9ngN_TCMbk7iqSgWQKkoFkA&h=9ad7b01c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4159589/org/dad4591925d640da304970224ea68a8f.jpg/jGvB9REH-K-4EbehYgoCULKZBZ2jVCUeLBxXECwcVxA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4159589%2Forg%2Fdad4591925d640da304970224ea68a8f.jpg%2FjGvB9REH-K-4EbehYgoCULKZBZ2jVCUeLBxXECwcVxA&h=cbf351ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發於昨（14日）晚上10時01分，將軍澳彩明商場麥當勞對出，一名56歲男子突然暈倒地上，昏迷不醒，有人報警求助。救護員接報到場，即場為其進行心外壓急救，並將他送往將軍澳醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n本身是註冊護士的中西區區議員任嘉兒剛好途經現場，救護員當時尚未到場，她立即上前為事主急救。她事後在facebook上發文講述事件，呼籲市民報讀急救課程。她指出，事發時傷者已全無反應，暈在地上，雖然圍觀者眾，但似乎無人懂得急救，未見有人接近傷者。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>任嘉兒﹕未進行檢查不應胡亂移動傷者</strong><br />\n<br />\n任嘉兒遂上前了解情況，發現傷者左眼眉骨流血，懷疑他曾向前跌倒受傷，血流滿地。任嘉兒指「未做任何檢查而胡亂移動傷者是唔可以的」，她脫下傷者口罩及眼鏡，觀察傷者情況及現場環境，估計對方是剛下班的保安員，他向前跌倒的狀態，相信脊椎未有受傷。傷者左眼眉骨傷口沒有再大量流血，身體其他部位目測沒有出血位。她曾呼喚傷者「先生先生」，但對方未有太大反應，但仍有微弱的呼吸及脈搏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4159567/org/8c45f8fe11f619aedd9d614b6bc31654.jpg/n0JHy5gIA4c5smF0sM8q-mC8qLQ39StbDN1jKwzdYys\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4159567%2Forg%2F8c45f8fe11f619aedd9d614b6bc31654.jpg%2Fn0JHy5gIA4c5smF0sM8q-mC8qLQ39StbDN1jKwzdYys&h=28602c1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男子在彩明商場內暈倒。（網民Ian Chan上傳）<br />\n<br />\n由於一人難以進行救援，任嘉兒向在場人士求助，幸有兩名懂急救的熱心男途人上前協助。三人合力將傷者者轉為復原卧式，即是打側身體，任嘉兒解釋，該姿勢可防止傷者的舌頭後墜，阻塞氣道；亦方便口腔內的分泌物或嘔吐物從口中流出，減低氣道受阻的機會。然後，他們鬆開傷者的領帶、頸繩，發現其脈搏微弱，開始沒有呼吸，對光線、聲音、痛楚沒有反應。<br />\n<br />\n情況轉趨危急，任嘉兒大叫「AED機（自動體外心臟去顫器）」，但現場無人能提供。她最終在多名熱心途人協助後，將傷者躺平，解開衣鈕，各人交替及進行心外壓搶救。未幾救護員接報到場，接手進行心外壓，並使用AED機分析心律，進行一次電擊，之後由救護車將傷者送院。據網民指，救護車在晚上約10時21分離開商場。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>呼籲港人報讀急救課程　增急救知識助救人</strong><br />\n<br />\n任嘉兒接受《香港01》記者電話訪問時表示，當時情況危急，而且不知傷者暈倒多久，分秒必爭下，她即時在現場檢查傷者情況後，便決定進行心外壓。對於不少人可能礙於疫情而不敢救援，她指留意到國內外及香港有不少暈倒失救的情況，認為不少個案是因缺氧而暈倒，嚴重則可能是急性中風、心臟病發等，心臟病在香港更是最常見的致命疾病中居第三位，「遲幾分鐘，生存率會好低，一開始就搓，可能會救得返。」因此她當下未有遲疑，即時救人。她亦呼籲港人報讀急救課程，例如聖約翰救傷隊、紅十字會舉辦的課程，「多啲急救知識，就可以快啲救到人。」<br />\n<br />\n領展回應事件表示，昨晚約10時， 1名年約60歲男子於彩明商場的自動櫃員機等候期間突然暈倒，途人發現時已報警，商場保安員亦即時到場協助。而警員和救護員到場後，為傷者進行急救並送往醫院診治。其後商場職員圍封現場並進行消毒。該名男子並非領展職員及保安員。<br />\n<br />\n另外，現時彩明商場並未設有「自動體外心臟去顫器」供職員使用。然而領展會不時檢視旗下物業的營運管理，致力提升設施及服務。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：楊婉婷"},{"pid":"8fb3c2ecb631ed11938655d25dc4825ecb8dceca","tid":1927314,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"咁大對奶都紅唔起！？"},{"pid":"e4e05b2fe34ed4f51e83bcfa27b0e743fff51f00","tid":1927314,"uid":286897,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"民主派區議員救人一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奶共派區議員謀財害命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0470124a243780f880393da145016e9ef3fd1c29","tid":1927314,"uid":13503,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"普通商場邊有AED<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d37c28c5d9a5e0be5faece96738090b8900018a","tid":1927314,"uid":42521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:10:14.000Z","msg":"幾時立法所有商場要有AED?"},{"pid":"8cf8a43d0bc85de8db681a65287396d09fabec9a","tid":1927314,"uid":138051,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"領展咁大間都冇AED... 呢部機基本要有啦"},{"pid":"64f40d499a1407659e73f3f68ca2b23d15375eec","tid":1927314,"uid":221055,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8cf8a43d0bc85de8db681a65287396d09fabec9a","tid":1927314,"uid":138051,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"領展咁大間都冇AED... 呢部機基本要有啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"部機好似都唔係貴，簡直應該大型公共建築物一定要有啦"},{"pid":"577bb7ca698dc6ff2c12edf9e999bd2f03a798b6","tid":1927314,"uid":29514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"領展收人咁貴租AED都無部，希望下次係支持領匯上市既廢老出事"},{"pid":"9b790e686d4990c2d9336d54c101f539ebafdf53","tid":1927314,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"疫情係問題<br />\n但無啦啦瞓低<br />\n你乜都唔知點幫佢?<br />\n整死佢邊搞?"},{"pid":"ba3b1d9dd7eb451e1d211c6b41aafe6683488eac","tid":1927314,"uid":63779,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9b790e686d4990c2d9336d54c101f539ebafdf53","tid":1927314,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"疫情係問題<br />\n但無啦啦瞓低<br />\n你乜都唔知點幫佢?<br />\n整死佢邊搞?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"係免刑架，只要係正常動機都唔會告得入。"},{"pid":"1d2a84bb3d8323399f05b9230d73f9828955f058","tid":1927314,"uid":31185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9b790e686d4990c2d9336d54c101f539ebafdf53","tid":1927314,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"疫情係問題<br />\n但無啦啦瞓低<br />\n你乜都唔知點幫佢?<br />\n整死佢邊搞?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:28:37.000Z","msg":"所以佢咪叫人學急救<br />\n同埋好似上面講咁商場要增設AED機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b44c602ebf36992d0d750adec2cb7fe8c2ff61","tid":1927314,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位朋友, 幫手發這個聯署出去, 幫手找人簽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=caae9bcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic</a><br />\n這個聯署是請求白宮要求youtube解釋為什麼限制談及武漢肺炎的題目? 為什麼限制言論自由? 希望大家幫手發出去, 因為被黃標了, 會影響收入, 是中共打壓言論自由的手段之一, 不可以就這樣被人打壓"},{"pid":"0bd12bda5978fa87520ac13069f54195945b0d1d","tid":1927314,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:35:53.000Z","msg":"香港人，pussy !"},{"pid":"ed7a35761b113b782eafe53b550af2d1033906c1","tid":1927314,"uid":42379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:43:56.000Z","msg":"真係天使，救人一命 勝造七級浮屠"},{"pid":"1fbcc2e15557f82832fc60189f5e639697a39a7a","tid":1927314,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"我見到任b都即刻昏迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ef07d20460914ed869430b02664d2820dfe6cd","tid":1927314,"uid":29792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"AED都冇！咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0b9ca8550137da38c4b452e118d415a779a7c0","tid":1927314,"uid":196701,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:10:39.000Z","msg":"樣衰(特別係對苦瓜眼)不過幾大波"},{"pid":"ae4e328a9ebeff4e730aff32f41007c974a75519","tid":1927314,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:43:28.000Z","msg":"掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0bc68caea1bf76cd0231b09c0d5502b0ce3adf","tid":1927314,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba3b1d9dd7eb451e1d211c6b41aafe6683488eac","tid":1927314,"uid":63779,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9b790e686d4990c2d9336d54c101f539ebafdf53","tid":1927314,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"疫情係問題<br />\n但無啦啦瞓低<br />\n你乜都唔知點幫佢?<br />\n整死佢邊搞?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"係免刑架，只要係正常動機都唔會告得入。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"其實有無刑罰唔係嗰下會考慮到嘅咩<br />\n會驚累死人<br />\n考完first aids都未必敢用"}]}